ARM: dts: sun4i: Enable i2c1 and i2c2 on the Chuwi V7-CW0825 tablet

i2c1 has a freescale mma7660 accelerometer connected to it at addr 0x4c,
i2c2 has a ft5x touchscreen connected to it at addr 0x38.

